				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It runs for me (I padded the CHR ROM using a .dsb directive). How big is your &quot;Graphics.chr&quot; file? It should be 8 kB (8192 byte) to fill out all of the CHR ROM space.<br /><br />This is unrelated, but I also noticed that your NMI- and IRQ-handlers are not ending in RTI instructions. Without an RTI they won't be able to return back to the main code after they have finished, and your game will not work as you want.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

