						<div class="postbody">Next time, do this when necessary:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">OPC $nn ;ZP mode, Optimal</div> instead of: <div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">OPC $00nn ;THIS IS RUBBISH!!!</div><br /><br />This way it is optimized by using the Zero Page model for opcodes instead of Absolute, It makes a BIG difference in your code when doing this<br /><br />OPC is an example opcode, Not really a valid 65-series opcode!</div>

					
